description	"HK-47

Class Summary: 
Heavily armored sniper and assassin equipt to terminate force wielders. 

Weaponry:
- Heavy Melee
- Droid Assassin's Rifle (Based on EE-3 level 3)
- Frag Grenades (2)
- Sonic Detonator (1)
- Trip Mine (1)
- Poison Darts (2)
- Wrist-Mounted Flamethrower (Class Special 2)
- Wrist Laser (Class Special 2)

Holdables:
- Cloaking Device
- Portable Sentry Gun

Attributes:
- Fuel (2)
- Regenerating Shields (1)
- Immune to Mind Trick
- Immune to Force Sense
- Magnetic Plating
- Blast Armor
- Cortosis Armor
- Melee Damage Resistance

HK-47 was a Hunter-Killer assassin droid and Jedi hunter constructed by the Dark Lord of the Sith, Darth Revan, shortly after the end of the Mandalorian Wars in 3960 BBY. HK-47 was sent throughout the galaxy on his missions and successfully assassinated countless targets whom Revan had deemed threats to galactic stability and peace."